{"title":"最大团","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":125,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-6582","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p style='font-family: \"Segoe UI\", \"Lucida Grande\", Helvetica, Arial, \"Microsoft YaHei\", FreeSans, Arimo, \"Droid Sans\", \"wenquanyi micro hei\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Hiragino Sans GB W3\", FontAwesome, sans-serif;'>数轴上有 n 个点,第 i 个点的坐标为 xi,权值为 wi。</p><p style='font-family: \"Segoe UI\", \"Lucida Grande\", Helvetica, Arial, \"Microsoft YaHei\", FreeSans, Arimo, \"Droid Sans\", \"wenquanyi micro hei\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Hiragino Sans GB W3\", FontAwesome, sans-serif;'>两个点 i,j 之间存在一条边当且仅当 abs(xi-xj)&gt;=wi+wj。</p><p style='font-family: \"Segoe UI\", \"Lucida Grande\", Helvetica, Arial, \"Microsoft YaHei\", FreeSans, Arimo, \"Droid Sans\", \"wenquanyi micro hei\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Hiragino Sans GB W3\", FontAwesome, sans-serif;'>你需要求出这张图的最大团的点数。</p><p style='font-family: \"Segoe UI\", \"Lucida Grande\", Helvetica, Arial, \"Microsoft YaHei\", FreeSans, Arimo, \"Droid Sans\", \"wenquanyi micro hei\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Hiragino Sans GB W3\", FontAwesome, sans-serif;'>(团就是两两之间有边的顶点集合)</p><p><br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span style='font-family: \"Segoe UI\", \"Lucida Grande\", Helvetica, Arial, \"Microsoft YaHei\", FreeSans, Arimo, \"Droid Sans\", \"wenquanyi micro hei\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Hiragino Sans GB W3\", FontAwesome, sans-serif;'>第一行一个整数 n,接下来 n 行每行两个整数 xi,wi。</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\">一行一个整数表示答案</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<pre style='font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, \"Courier New\", FontAwesome, monospace;'>4\n2 3\n3 1\n6 1\n0 2</pre><p><br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>3</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p style='font-family: \"Segoe UI\", \"Lucida Grande\", Helvetica, Arial, \"Microsoft YaHei\", FreeSans, Arimo, \"Droid Sans\", \"wenquanyi micro hei\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Hiragino Sans GB W3\", FontAwesome, sans-serif;'>对于 20%的数据,n&lt;=10。</p><p style='font-family: \"Segoe UI\", \"Lucida Grande\", Helvetica, Arial, \"Microsoft YaHei\", FreeSans, Arimo, \"Droid Sans\", \"wenquanyi micro hei\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Hiragino Sans GB W3\", FontAwesome, sans-serif;'>对于 60%的数据,n&lt;=1000。</p><p style='font-family: \"Segoe UI\", \"Lucida Grande\", Helvetica, Arial, \"Microsoft YaHei\", FreeSans, Arimo, \"Droid Sans\", \"wenquanyi micro hei\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Hiragino Sans GB W3\", FontAwesome, sans-serif;'>对于 100%的数据,n&lt;=200000,0&lt;=|xi|,wi&lt;=10^9</p><p><br></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}